                    <gco:CharacterString>Soil moisture is retrieved over land targets on the descending (AM) SMAP half-orbits when the SMAP spacecraft is travelling from North to South, while the SMAP instruments are operating in the nominal mode.  The L3_SM_P product represents soil moisture retrieved over the entre UTC day.
